</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200826/99c6554a6bae45b599af6d5486e39a47.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>食材</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">蛋糕底：奥利奥碎180g、黄油90g</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">慕斯煳：酸奶400g、淡奶油400g、白糖40g、吉利丁4片（20g）、杨梅汁少许</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水果布丁层：杨梅汁适量、吉利丁5g</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">装饰：糖渍杨梅适量、薄荷适量</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200826/a9c08f0720de4a329e65f56e8eeb5a17.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>步骤</strong></h1>
<p>黄油隔热水融化。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200826/112a542deee142cab4c6c899efedd3e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">奥利奥放入保鲜袋中用擀面杖压碎，越碎越好。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200826/0f58aa8e4a0c426b813a934ffbef8956.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">融化成液态的黄油倒入奥利奥碎中。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/94554852c43c4e1faa4cec19307c3f2b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">搅拌均匀直奥利奥碎完全吸收黄油。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200826/229618ea86434a8a9ad07d0dbd940b05.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200826/b55bec6d7d5b425a9e36abee8b96e943.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">取八寸圆模，将奥利奥碎倒入。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200826/88d3d027e5c948ceae4c7bf8ea547141.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">用勺子压平压实，蛋糕底完成。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200826/1d29d746413a4658baca3b604acff807.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">放入冰箱冷冻一小时。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200826/9e7e8ec05e96446bb506a247382b52d4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">吉利丁片4片（20g）冰水中泡软，差不多需要5分钟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200826/88af8486b273461eafb7d8df1ecc45ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">加入酸奶中，慢慢搅拌直吉利丁融化，可以用打蛋器搅打融化的快一些。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200826/749bfed02d6447b59bd80215ec7da583.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">奶油中加白糖。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200826/08a518abee6d4eba9f9d30ff66829573.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">打蛋器低速打发。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200826/7479681a72424bed8c0dd4207ff3f7fa.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">打至奶油出现轻微痕迹滴落不会马上消失即可。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200826/cd62e9183ccf4efcb470d0cb38bf9470.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">将酸奶液和奶油混合均匀，原味慕斯煳完成。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/fd32e8d41e284618b5fa92d0e228b3bd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200826/2b4bc73eacd64485814b141fb341ada0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">取一部分慕斯煳，加入少量杨梅汁，将慕斯煳调成粉色。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200826/434760b1c59d491085c45d4178fcf5e5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">从冰箱里取出刚才做好的蛋糕底。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">剩下的慕斯煳倒入，稍稍晃一晃至均匀，放入冰箱冷藏30分钟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200826/5ae3a21c45d4490dab7d5a75675c5114.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">5g吉利丁冰水中泡软。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200826/af45893942f547af82283fb654bc948e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">加入杨梅汁液中至融化。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200826/8599b7fadade46e9bab68a8a259d0e62.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">30分钟后，取出刚才做好的蛋糕半成品，将做好的杨梅汁液倒入。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">再次放入冰箱冷藏30分钟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200826/e66f66942e4b447aab19ac270cbc915a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">30分钟后将蛋糕模具取出，把刚才做好的粉红色的慕斯煳倒入，放入冰箱冷藏1小时即可。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200826/5dbac150ecf44c11a4009856adb68e8c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">做好的慕斯蛋糕用热毛巾在周围敷一敷，或者电吹风热风吹一圈，就可以轻松脱模啦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200826/c498a1c915e24412ac178c7e5b34d2f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">根据喜好放上糖渍杨梅和薄荷做装饰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200826/fedeabe8af4042b4a4df3ee9931ca446.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">小清新，看起来很清爽呀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/890c3f69dbab430ea4f615717833f267.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">杨梅酸奶慕斯完成！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200826/c14b2734a1a64244bec3241789ece9fa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">放上喜欢的装饰品，做成生日蛋糕的样子。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200826/0887a93b370042b2ac07d82a63f7766f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">生日快乐呦～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200826/80c5649c4f674cb492cf31a8fa723e76.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>小贴士</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-justify">1、慕斯蛋糕中还可以加入奶油奶酪，奶香味更浓，做出来口感会更加嫩滑。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">2、慕斯底不一定非要用奥利奥，也可以用消化饼干。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3、吉利丁粉可以换成吉利丁片，自行转换量即可。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">4、雪碧可以提前摇一摇，等消气后再加入吉利丁溶液搅拌，或者静置一会让其消气。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">5、蛋糕脱模以后再放冰箱冷藏一会让其凝固更好。</p>
<p><strong>图文：</strong>呵呵笋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200826/54eb8943284b4ab987572616c9acdcc9.png" max-width="600" /></p>
